<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu khut a kan sak ui, Huona a paucham petin,
 Zahhuoi in kawtthel a puiin;
 Hukdampa chilsiet khum in,
 Gitloh bei leh thiengtho, kilhden un thiemloh ti'n a gen ui.

[V2]
 A sam thei hi Angel sangsawm te,
 Leisiet susie a Amah tan di'n;
 A sam thei hi Angel sangsawm te,
 Mahleh, A thi tai nang leh kei di'n.

[V3]
 2. A lu thiengtho tak chungah linglukhuk a kawih ui,
 Nuihsan in 'Lengpa en un&quot; ti'n;
 Sapsiet na tawh zep kawm in,
 Amin thiengtho nuihsan in, Amah maiin bang cheng a thuok tai.

[V4]
 3. Kross a a kilhden lai un, Anu a kawma ding,
 &quot;Numei na chapa en in&quot; ti'n; Tui ka duh&quot; ti'n ka kiko;
 Kuoma'n dawn ding a pie puoi,
 Mihiem gitloh nasep a zo tai.

[V5]
 4. Mi gilote kawma kipie'n, Zahngaihna a ngen puoi,
 Kross zahhuoi amah mai a pu'n;
 &quot;Zawh ei tai&quot; ti'n a kiko,
 Thi dingin a kipie a, Hukdamna mak tak chuh A zo tai.</lyrics>
<title>TEN THOUSAND ANGELS</title>
<hymn_number>182</hymn_number>
</song>